## Verification Rules

- **VERIFIED**: Has a source URL or document reference. Empirical fact.
- **ASSUMED**: Reasonable belief based on experience. MUST be flagged.
- **UNCERTAIN**: Conflicting information found. Needs expert input.
- **OUTDATED**: Was verified but source is older than 12 months. Re-verify.
